Leighton HarrisFund Operations
Working at Orbis is not for everyoneIt is imperative that our people can thrive in an environment of individual accountability and our flat management structure emphasises contribution over seniority.At Orbis, we seek to attract highly motivated individuals who share our Core Values. This applies not only in investment management but in everything that we do, from client service to back-office operations. We aim to give our people the resources they need to succeed and the rest is up to them. While we expect our people to have outstanding academic credentials we also look for evidence of success outside the classroom in whatever they have done. We also place great value in demonstrated courage to think independently, even if it means disagreeing with the rest of the team. Our flat management structure emphasises contribution over seniority meaning that an individual’s progression and reward is completely dependent on their ability to add value.Meet Our People to watch more profiles.Contact OrbisOrbis AccessMedia EnquiriesAccessibilityOrbis Investment Management Limited © 2017
