Simon SkinnerEquity Analyst
Leighton HarrisFund Operations
Working at Orbis is not for everyoneIt is imperative that our people can thrive in an environment of individual accountability and our flat management structure emphasises contribution over seniority.At Orbis, we seek to attract highly motivated individuals who share our Core Values. This applies not only in investment management but in everything that we do, from client service to back-office operations. We aim to give our people the resources they need to succeed and the rest is up to them. While we expect our people to have outstanding academic credentials we also look for evidence of success outside the classroom in whatever they have done. We also place great value in demonstrated courage to think independently, even if it means disagreeing with the rest of the team. Our flat management structure emphasises contribution over seniority meaning that an individual’s progression and reward is completely dependent on their ability to add value.Meet Our People to watch more profiles.Contact OrbisOrbis AccessMedia EnquiriesAccessibilityOrbis Investment Management Limited © 2017


Orbis Investment Management Limited: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 27, 2017 12:20 PM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Orbis Investment Management Limited



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Orbis Investment Management Limited is a privately owned investment manager. The firm provides its services to institutions and individuals. It manages separate client focused equity and balanced portfolios. The firm also manages equity and balanced mutual funds. It invests in the public equity and fixed income markets across the globe including non-US markets, Asia ex-Japan, and Japan. For its equity investments, the firm invests in value stock of companies. It employs fundamental and quantitative analysis with a focus on bottom-up approach to make its investments. The firm benchmarks the performance of its portfolios against various MSCI indices, TOPIX, and JP Morgan Global Government Bond...
Orbis Investment Management Limited is a privately owned investment manager. The firm provides its services to institutions and individuals. It manages separate client focused equity and balanced portfolios. The firm also manages equity and balanced mutual funds. It invests in the public equity and fixed income markets across the globe including non-US markets, Asia ex-Japan, and Japan. For its equity investments, the firm invests in value stock of companies. It employs fundamental and quantitative analysis with a focus on bottom-up approach to make its investments. The firm benchmarks the performance of its portfolios against various MSCI indices, TOPIX, and JP Morgan Global Government Bond Index. It was founded in 1989 and is based in Hamilton, Bermuda. Orbis Investment Management Limited operates as a subsidiary of Orbis Group.
Detailed Description


