Alvin holds a Bachelor of Applied Science and Engineering (High Honours), University of Toronto, and graduated in the top 5% of his class as a Baker Scholar from the Master of Business Administration at...
View full bio



Alvin holds a Bachelor of Applied Science and Engineering (High Honours), University of Toronto, and graduated in the top 5% of his class as a Baker Scholar from the Master of Business Administration at Harvard University.  
Prior to joining Orbis in 2010, he was an Engagement Manager with McKinsey & Company in Hong Kong, and before that a Program Manager with Microsoft in Seattle.  Alvin has also previously founded a software startup and was granted two patents by the US Patent Office.





 






